Product name: Antique Child's Sled, Antique Toddler Sled, Primitive Toy, Rustic Christmas Decor, Primitive Christmas Decor, c. 1870-1899, FREE SHIPPING
Description:
This is a handmade wood antique toddler sled. This antique child's sled would make a stunning addition to any rustic Christmas decor or primitive Christmas decor. Although you wouldn't use this primitive toy for its original purpose today, it would make an amazing Christmas centerpiece, plant stand, or display piece. It would look great on a porch or by a fireplace, among many other possibilities for winter decor. This rustic sled is believed to have come over from Europe in the late 1800s. The old chippy green paint on this 1800s toy appears to be original. This primitive sled is jointed together and has small metal supports, possibly hand-forged, which can be seen at the base of its two front legs. (I believe the supports are original because the old paint is covering them.) This antique toy measures approximately 22" long x 11" wide x 11" high.
This is a vintage item with the natural wear, tear, and character flaws of age. It has many wonderful imperfections, such as a big crack in the back, uneven edges and planes, chippy paint, a visible white drop of paint, exposed metal supports (some with the green paint wearing off), scuffed edges, etc, but somehow all of it just seems to add to this wonderful antique toy's aged charm. Please see the photos for condition, as they are part of the description.
ADDITIONAL IMPORTANT INFO:
You will receive the exact sled shown in the photos above. (The teddy bear and poinsettia are not included.)
Please respect that prices are firm. Free Shipping is included to the United States & U.S. territories American Samoa, Guam, Northern Mariana Islands, Puerto Rico, and U.S. Virgin Islands. 
For repeat customers, I am happy to reserve an item for up to 24 hours.
The items I sell are vintage and are being sold as collector's items rather than as usable items intended for their original purpose. These items are not new or pristine. They have the wear, tear, and flaws of age, and it's in that used, aged condition that you are buying them. I will point out any flaws that I notice, but please study the photos carefully as I consider them to be a big part of the item description. Also please ask questions, which I will be happy to answer to the best of my ability. Keep in mind that while I may sell vintage items and antiques, I am not an expert, so you need to rely on your own judgment when making a purchase.
***OHIO SALES TAX***
I am required by state law to charge sales tax of 7.25% to residents of OHIO on the total cost of their purchase, including shipping.
Please see my Shipping & Policies page for more important details.
THANK YOU FOR YOUR PATRONAGE!

Description:
======== DESCRIPTION ========
Secure your luggage with these handmade personalized leather luggage tag(s) which are also great gifts for any traveling man/woman. I only use Grade A premium leather from Hermann Oak so these tags are sure to last the life of your luggage bags.
======== WHAT YOU'LL RECEIVE ========

======== PRODUCT FEATURES ========
   - 2 inches tall, 4 inches wide 
   - Thick 8/9oz (~3.5mm or 1/8 inch) Hermann Oak Leather
   - Mahogany dyed edges
   - Smoothed/burnished edges
   - Saddle Tan stained color
   - Silver metal cable and matching grommet
   - Unique custom font for engraving
======== PERSONALIZATION INSTRUCTIONS ========
   - Add your engraving instructions in the "Notes To Seller" section during checkout
   - Maximum 5 lines
   - Select combination of 2 font sizes
      - Large: 12 characters per line
      - Small: 16 characters per line
   - Spaces count as characters 
   - Characters allowed
      - CAPITAL letters [A-Z]
      - Numbers [0-9]
      - single quote '
      - comma ,
      - dash -
      - double quote "
      - ampersand & 
      - at symbol @ 
      - exclamation point ! 
      - pound sign #
      - period .
      - dollar sign 
      - parentheses ( )
      - question mark ?
      - degree °
======== PRODUCTION & DELIVERY TIME ========
   - Regular production & shipping schedule
      - Production time: 3 business days
      - Shipping time: 3 business days
   - Rush order production & shipping schedule
      - Production time: 2 business days
      - Shipping time: 1 business day
======== BUILD QUALITY ========
I've spent a full 2.5 years making strictly just luggage tags and have developed the process and technique to deliver you the best product that I personally can. Many customers have expressed that they are incredibly happy with the customer service and end result of their unique luggage tag.
Each tag is carefully: 
  - tooled with your inscription
  - stained a saddle tan color for a more vintage & rustic look
  - edges dyed and burnished for a more professional finish
  - applied with a water-resistant cream for longevity and protection
  - secured with a metal grommet and leather strap for better security
======== RELATED ITEMS ========
If you'd like order a pair of these to save some money, please see the following listing:

Black Metal Wire Cable & Grommet

Gold Metal Wire Cable & Grommet
https://www.etsy.com/listing/503285250
Leather Strap & Silver Grommet
https://www.etsy.com/listing/195568643
======== FAQs ========
"Can you give me a quote for a large order?"
   - Absolutely! I love working with people and managing larger orders (wedding favors, family gifts, etc).
"Does the leather strap come with each tag?"
    - Yep! Each tag comes with the leather strap attached to the tag.
"Can you stamp anything on the back?"
    - Unfortunately, I cannot. The back side (flesh side) of the leather is rough and will leave and impression on the front if tooled on.
"Do you have any other colors available?"
   - I only have a single color stain (saddle tan) but can accommodate for larger orders.
"How soon will the order get to me?"
   - It depends if you're domestic (lower 48 states) or international. Allow 2-3 business days for shipping and 5-6 business days for international orders.

Following is a little of what I found about these.
Hazel Atlas Glass	
Ovide (Platonite) Ovide was the official name Hazel Atlas assigned to their plain dinnerware line. Originally, the dinnerware was made in green transparent (depression glass). After the introduction of Platonite in the mid 1930s, Hazel Atlas produced a variety of color schemes using the Ovide blanks.
Some pieces in Ovide are found with advertising from ice cream parlors, businesses, dairies and an occasional restaurant. The ovide style was also used for all the spacemen, childrens, and Ranger Joe sets.

The advantages of Vintage Bling over modern bling are: 
1) no-one else will be wearing it, 
2) it holds it's value, when you fancy a change you can sell it on and replace with a different 'new to you' piece, 
3) it is environmentally friendly because no new resources are being used to make, 
4) it's the opposite to throwaway fashion, no child is working in slave labour conditions to make something which'll fall apart or you wear once,
and finally, 5) the fact it is still in serviceable condition after 80 years means it was made to a quality that lasts.

Product name: Antique I Ching Coins from Bali, Genuine Coins, Brocade Purses F2005.P3040 *
Description:
Antique Chinese I Ching coins. These are the real deal; brought to the US in the '70's from Bali, Indonesia, not an imitation or modern replica. 
* The Balinese used the coins for funerary purposes and in ceremonial designs (masks, etc.). They are of different ages, and the Chinese writing on the coins varies depending on age. They can be left as is, or rubbed to a soft warm brass color. 
*The Coins have passed thru many hands in their long history, and it is important that you make them yours before you use them. Sleep with them under your pillow for at least one week. 
Note: For each I Ching set, the Coins will be as different in size and markings as possible. For Top Drilled Set, the two coins will be matched as to size.
The Earrings shown(not part of sale--just for ideas)are made from top drilled Ching coins.
* Choose One Set of Three Random I Ching coins (undrilled) or One Set of Two Matched Coins with top hole drilled, for earrings, amulets or pendants. The coins are all around 3/4-7/8-1 inch round.
YOU WILL RECEIVE: Your Choice of One, or Two Sets of THREE ASSORTED Coins for casting the I Ching OR TWO MATCHED Drilled Coins. 
Three Coin set for casting the I Ching comes in a Brocade Presentation purse.
***CHINESE "BROCADE" PURSE POUCH FOR JEWELRY P3040
*Available separately, Charming little multi-color Chinese Brocade Pattern Purses, with a zippered pouch for Earring gift giving. Size is 2 1/2 inches by 3 inches; suitable for earrings, a ring, small pendant on a chain necklace or a piece of jewelry that you want to store carefully.

Product name: Enid Collins Box Bag - Enid Collins "Love" Box Bag - Enid Collins - Collins of Texas - Enid Collins Handbag - Enid Collins Purse
Description:
Fun and fabulous Enid Collins box bag.  This wonderful handbag was made in the 1960's by Collins of Texas, the company started by Enid Collins.  The "Love" line of wood box bags is highly collectible and is found in a few different designs.  The most popular are the ones that feature this pastel pink, green, yellow, and white decoration.  The color palette and "love" message were a big hit in the hippie influenced fashion scene of the late 1960's.  Some of the bags had leather handles, some had a hard plastic or a flexible vinyl handle. 
Measurements - 5 1/2" tall  x  8 1/2"  x  4 1/4".
Very good vintage condition.  A few minor scrapes and wear, interior very clean.  Vinyl handle and interior mirror in very good condition.  One missing flower embellishment.

Product name: China stamps 9 mint old
Description:
Nice almost complete collection of rare old  stamps honoring Sun Yat Sen
           41 VALUE  FOR ONLY 23.99. This collection was purchased    successfully from a major estate           
                        
    Sun Yat Sen ; 12 November 1866 – 12 March 1925) was a Chinese revolutionary, first president and founding father of the Republic of China, and medical practitioner. As the foremost pioneer of the Republic of China, Sun is referred to as the "Father of the Nation" in the Republic of China (ROC), and the "forerunner of democratic revolution" in the People's Republic of China (PRC). Sun played an instrumental role in the overthrow of the Qing dynasty during the years leading up to the Double Ten Revolution. He was appointed to serve as Provisional President of the Republic of China when it was founded in 1912. He later co-founded the Kuomintang (KMT), serving as its first leader.[3] Sun was a uniting figure in post-Imperial China, and he remains unique among 20th-century Chinese politicians for being widely revered amongst the people from both sides of the Taiwan Strait.
     Sun's chief legacy resides in his developing of the political philosophy known as the Three Principles of the People: nationalism (non-ethnic, independence from imperialist domination), democracy (up to Western standards), and the people's livelihood by instituting free trade and Georgist tax reform

A stunning vintage 1970's UNUSED 100% wool hallmarked Mr. John's hat. It is from his Classics Paris/New York collection made for Saks Fifth Avenue Department Store. It has an exquisite shape. NOTE: Mr. John was John Harberger (1906-1993) was one of the foremost milliners of the 20th century. He began by working for his mother, Mme. Laurel, in 1926. In 1929 he formed his company  under John-Frederics. He designed hats for the movies, probably the most famous being those made for Vivien Leigh in Gone with the Wind.Mr. John hats were produced through the 1970's & under private label through the 1980's.

Also available to choose are the Strange Companion Blends, which are color-coded on the bottoms of the vials instead of a wrap around label:

Coffee  Cocoa - (warm, sweet, indulgent, comforting, gourmand)

Palo Santo  Amyris - (sharp, spicy, bold, woods, smooth drydown)

(See the regular-sized versions of these products in my shop for full descriptions.) 
• Each vial contains at least 0.5mL of perfume - enough for about 3 applications. (this means each vial will be at least half-filled with perfume since their full capacity is 1mL.)
• Packaged inside a small (1 3/4" x 1" x 1/2") gift box. Each vial is about 1.5'' long.
• A descriptive card about the scent and a list of the prominent notes and accords is included for each perfume.
About Natural Perfume:
If you have used synthetically fragranced products (fragrance oils), you have probably noticed how they are missing the depth and the true scent that real plants, fruits, and flowers have. 
Natural perfumes are much different to wear than what you will find at a headache-inducing commercial perfume counter; these essences meld with your body chemistry and stay close to the skin. Only you and those you embrace will be aware that you are wearing it. These blends of botanical distillations are more satisfying to the senses and have subtle healing properties (aromatherapy) that your mind and body will love.
Combined in a base of organic jojoba and coconut oil, these perfumes nourish the skin instead of damaging it as alcohol-based perfumes do. They also do not contain chemicals to make them last all day. Instead, they wear off in the course of about 4-6 hours, and can be re-applied as a sensory ritual. This allows the opportunity to reflect and appreciate the moment, connect with nature through its true essences, and experience the perfume’s evolution in intervals each day.
© For Strange Women.
*Keep out of direct sunlight and high temperatures.
• 100% natural. phthalate, paraben, synthetic, alcohol, petroleum, and cruelty free.

Description:
Your choice of 3 all natural solid perfume samples and get at least one extra random pot of perfume included as a gift.  Perfumes created with pure essential oils and made with either beeswax or plant wax. All natural pure plant essences that are of premium quality, and cruelty free. the P E R F U M E S...
Ambra - Unisex. Fossilized amber with its earthy, woodsy note, my own blended amber, with cistus, vetiver, and forest notes. My original Amber themed perfume.
An Island for Paula - tropical fruit notes amongst soft notes of Mimosa and Lotus. A sweet tropical experience.
Belles - A big splash of citrus in a delicious blend of Vanilla, Turkish Rose, Faint Jasmine, wildflowers and a dash of saffron.
Dreaming Forest - Notes of  Moss, Canadian Fir, Balsam, Spruce, tree sap, and fossilized amber resin. I describe this one as the scent of  trees with a dash of smoke from the fireplace which is filled with crackling pinecones  and fir logs.
Driftwood - Dry parched woods with smooth dark, earthy notes.
Emiko - This perfume oil is a botanical inspiration. If you are a sci fi fan you will recognize the name perhaps, if not, the name Emiko comes from the original Godzilla story and the perfume itself is certainly inspired. Emiko contains delicious notes of mandarin and blood orange up front with coconut and dreamy apricot, along with subtle Japanese rose and a hint of creamy Gardenia on a base of vanilla bourbon which gives the perfume a lovely finish that isn't too sweet.
Eartha - Opens in a field of mushrooms then blends beautifully into creamy rich patchouli and sandalwood with hints of tuberose. Inspired by a story I am writing and also included in the Fragments of Darkness series of perfumes.
Loom of Smoke - Walk into the woods and breathe in the scented damp fog, dense fragrant moss, and towering woods. The other notes include tree bark, fir and pine veiled in faintest smoke, a hint of wild lavender, black currant, incense, fossilized amber, in pure grain alc tincture of 3000 yr old cedar bark.
Miss Mary Jane - inspired by a female botanist. Notes of champa flower, faint plumeria, lightest peach note with incense, faintly smokey, sandalwood base. From the Lady Botanists series.
Tobacco Rose - Vintage Rose and dry, sweet tobacco marry beautifully with soft saffron and creamy woods. 
Nine Days in July - Fresh air atop a bouquet of lotus and champa flower with a smooth sandalwood finish.
Poete Fleur - Seriously dirt-soil and daffodil. Very green and complimented with tonka bean.
Rosa d'orleans - This perfume's main note is French Rose married with amber and accented with notes of cardamom, black pepper, rock rose, siam wood blend, vetiver, and roots of iris. What French inspired perfume wouldn't have a dash of powder? just a dash....
Rosewood and Vetiver - Opens with the scent of wild berries on a bed of vetiver and rosewood
The Rose Bee - My personal fave right now with notes of honeycomb, beeswax, clover, and rose. A very honeycomb rose scent with notes of hay and clover added. Helps support pollinators!
Welcome to Siberia - the icy cold fir and pine forests of  trees.
.
Zelle Opium - Very spicy perfume, think opium dens of long ago with cinnamon, pepper, carnation, ylang,on a vetiver base. Very spicy.

Product name: Organic 100% Grass-fed Tallow Balm
Description:
Seasonal note: We are headed into the warm summer months! If your tallow balm appears melted upon arrival, just pop it into the refrigerator for a few hours, and it will solidify. Enjoy your summer! 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Add gift wrapping to any order! Just find gift wrapping listed as a separate product in my shop, and add it to your purchase.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Experience the deep nourishing properties of grass-fed tallow in this pure tallow balm. Essential in skin care, this balm moisturizes, heals, and protects skin like nothing else. Perfect as an anti-aging face cream, for healing and soothing dry or itchy skin, eczema, diaper rash, wind and sunburn, and for fading scars and stretch marks. 
My organic, 100% grass-fed tallow comes from cattle raised locally on pasture here in Loveland, Colorado. No antibiotics, hormones, or pesticides are used. Cattle eat only rotationally grazed grass, and are never fed any grain. I store my tallow in glass only. 
I use exclusively Plant Therapy® brand essential oils in my products. They are some of the highest quality essential oils available, and you can read about their purity, policies and practices at https://www.planttherapy.com/essential-oil-quality 
Ingredients:
100% Grass-fed beef tallow†, extra virgin olive oil*, therapeutic grade essential oils
*certified organic
†not certified organic, but raised according to and even beyond organic certification standards
Available as an amber glass jar.
Note: 100% grass-fed tallow has a softer consistency than tallow from cattle fed grain. This is a sign of the higher nutrient content, and evidence that the cattle were indeed fed and finished on only grass. You can expect 100% grass-fed tallow to be about the same consistency at room temperature as grass-fed butter: softer at warmer temperatures, and firmer at cooler temperatures. If you prefer a firmer product, but still want the nutrients and benefits of 100% grass-fed, consider storing it in a cool place.

Description:
🎊 This tutu is made with Red, Orange, Yellow, Emerald Green, Royal Blue and Purple Tulle. 🎊
Do you have a school function you would like to dress up for or even a fun run 5k like the Zombie Run, Turkey Trot or a Color Run?! Then this tutu is for you!! This Tutu is perfect for many occasions including holidays, dance classes, photo props, dress up, birthday parties and so much more!
The tutu is made with 3 layers of soft tulle and is hand tied onto a premade crochet band which is very stretchy. 
👀 The tutu may appear small first out of the package but the waistband is super stretchy and will stretch to the max measurement stated in the listing under the sizes. I always double and triple check my measurements so Please try it on first. Thank you! 
💥TUTU SIZES/LENGTHS:
Newborn - 12 months: The Tutu will measure 6" long
12 months - 24 months: The Tutu will measure 7" long
2T - 5T: The Tutu will measure 8" long or 9" long (2 choices)
 
📢📢PLEASE NOTE: Please measure around your HIPS as well as your WAIST and go by the biggest measurement when choosing which size you need. 
🚨EXAMPLE: if your waist is 28 inches but your hips are 35 inches, you will need to get a size that fits over the 35 inches. These tutus are pull on so they need to fit over the hips to get to your waist. If you do not have a measuring tape you can use a piece of string and measure that against a standard ruler. 
🎉🎊ALL SIZES LISTED BELOW ARE A STANDARD 9 INCHES LONG. 🎉🎊
 
GIRLS: Waist/Hip size 21 - 27" (max stretch) will be 9" in length (athletic length)
ADULT SMALL: Waist/Hip size 27 - 32" (max stretch) will be 9" in length (athletic length)
ADULT MEDIUM: Waist/Hip size 32 - 36" (max stretch) will be 9" in length (athletic length) 
ADULT LARGE: Waist/Hip size 36 - 40" (max stretch) will be 9" in length (athletic length)
ADULT XLARGE: Waist/Hip size 40 - 44" (max stretch) will be 9" in length (athletic length)
ADULT 2XLARGE: Waist/Hip size 44 - 48" (max stretch) will be 9" in length (athletic length)
🚨 PLEASE measure your HIPS too! 🚨
📢📢Please note that this is a general size guide that I use, they are not based on US pant sizes. 
❎EXAMPLE: If you can not get your size 30/31 waist pants on (all the way up from feet to waist) without unbuttoning and unzipping them first then a SMALL: 27 - 32" Max will NOT fit. 🚨Please double check your WAIST and HIP measurements before placing your order. For a custom fit please put both your hip and waist measurements in the notes to seller box. Thank you!

Product name: Handmade Intermediate Oboe Reed
Description:
One handmade intermediate level reed is shaped on a nagamtsu shaper tip, from an Innoledy gouge.  The reed tied on a 47mm MSA oboe staple and measures a total of 70-71mm.  This reed is great for advanced middle school students to intermediate high school students.  The reed is easy to play but still has a warm and rich sound.  All reeds I personally play-check for intonation, response, and excellent tone.
My first priority in reed making is to make the reed responsive and easy to play on, even in my professional level reeds.  Secondly I ensure that each reed consistently plays in tune at 440.  I am very careful to check the octaves in the upper register so the reed does not require pinching or biting to play in tune.  Once these two elements are present, a beautiful, warm, full sound always emerges.  
My reeds are superior because I am a band director. I have seen what works and what doesn't with beginning oboe students and advanced students. Before I began teaching in a school district, I only sold my reeds to my oboe students. Then I was able to fix a reed whenever a student was struggling with it. But now that I am directing a band program of over 250 students, I don't have time to adjust reeds every time I see my student. I have a very accurate picture of a student needs from their reed.  I ensure that it is complete and ready to play!
Here is a guide to help you select your reed type and strength
Beginner Medium/Soft Reed--These reeds are for beginners who are just learning to play or have only been playing a few months.  They are very easy to play but will not provide the mature tone that the intermediate or professional reeds will supply.  
www.etsy.com/listing/170185242/handmade-beginner-oboe-reed
Intermediate Medium Reed--If you are unsure of which reed to order, this is a great place to start.  These reeds will play "broken in" after very little use.  They are easy to play but still provide a mature sound and are a great follow up to the Beginning Medium/Soft reeds.  These reeds are great for any level, but are best for students who have been playing for 6 months- 3 or 4 years.  These reeds are completely finished and will not have much room for alterations.  
https://www.etsy.com/listing/170186238/handmade-intermediate-oboe-reed
Intermediate Medium/Hard Reed--These reeds are less responsive than the Intermediate Medium Reeds.  They have darker tone and have more room for you to tailor your reed to your playing style.  They have a thicker tip and will take more time to break them in. Students who order these reeds are advanced middle school students or freshmen or sophomores in High school. 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/170186238/handmade-intermediate-oboe-reed
Professional Medium Reed--The professional reeds have a nicer staple that really open the reeds up and sing beautifully.  The Medium reeds are the reeds that I would most likely play on myself and will play already "broken in".  
https://www.etsy.com/listing/170186400/handmade-professional-oboe-reed
Professional Medium/Hard Reed-- The professional reeds have a nicer staple that really open the reeds up and sing beautifully.  They have darker tone and have more room for you to tailor your reed to your playing style.  They have a thicker tip and will take more time to break them in. 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/170186400/handmade-professional-oboe-reed
Professional Hard Reed-- The professional reeds have a nicer staple that really open the reeds up and sing beautifully.  These reeds would be great for an oboist who feels that a Medium/Hard reed just isn't hard enough!!  They will have lots of room for adjustment and will be less responsive than the Medium/Hard reeds.  Buyer beware...these are hard! 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/170186400/handmade-professional-oboe-reed

Product name: Anniversary Gift, Custom Anniversary Gift, Personalized Anniversary Gift, 5th Anniversary Gift, Gift for Couple, Name Gift, Last Name Gift
Description:
Our engraved cutting board is the perfect combination of decorative design and practicality. We offer you the opportunity to give a special personalized gift to someone you love. This gift is especially perfect for newlyweds and new home owners!
ITEM DETAILS
• We currently offer Walnut or Maple in three different sizes: 7”x8”, 9”x12”, and 10.5”x16”. All boards are 3/4” thick. {Item pictured is Walnut 10.5"x16"}
• One side of the board will be engraved, the other side is left blank for use
• All boards are finished with a food grade mineral oil after engraving.
• Our boards are engraved with a laser. This means that the design is burned into the wood and may burn differently with varying depths and color depending on the consistency of the wood being used.
• Hand washing is our recommendation (not safe for dishwasher)
HOW TO ORDER
• Choose your size and wood preference from the drop down menu
• Add the item to your cart
• Leave your personalization details in the “Note to Seller” box at the bottom of the check-out page. This is the information we will need from you: 1- Last Name 2- Date Established
NOTE
• We are happy to make font changes. Please request so in the note to seller box.
• We are happy to provide a proof upon purchase. If you would like one, please request a proof along with your personalizations in the note to seller box at checkout.
PRODUCTION and SHIPPING
• 3-5 business days for production 
• 2-3 day USPS Priority Shipping for domestic orders
• First Class International for international orders (shipping times vary, buyer is responsible for any additional customs fees)
*Need it faster??*
Use this link to rush your order! 
http://etsy.me/2aLetxB
*Want to see our entire collection?*
 Click this link! 
http://etsy.me/1NNnEGK
PLEASE NOTE
The process of engraving a wood cutting board includes the use of a high density laser. The laser beam burns the wood, producing the desired design. Because each board’s wood is different (i.e.,the grain, texture, and consistency), the coloration of the engraving and grain pattern of the wood may be slightly different than the picture shown. 
We use a food grade mineral oil which seasons the wood, sealing out moisture and brings out the natural color and grain pattern of the wood. No wood stains are used.

Product name: Metal Stamp Symmetrical Branch Border (DS433)
Description:
Symmetrical Branch Border Metal Design Stamp - Beaducation Original
-Design measures: 11.5mm wide by 3.5mm high.
-Made from 1/2" square heat-treated tool steel.
-Arrive coated in oil to prevent rusting. 
-Wipe oil away with paper towel. Do not use water. 
-Use on typical jewelry metals, not on hard metals like Stainless Steel.
Lisa's Notes:
Design Stamps are a bit tricky. I highly recommend you practice on some cheaper metal before diving into your Sterling Silver or Gold Filled. You can also watch my FREE video tutorial, Stamping on Metal at www.beaducation.com/online_classes/20
For best results with Design Stamps, make sure there is NO padding under your Bench Block, make sure you are working on a stable table, and use a utility hammer (nail pounding hammer) which weighs at least 16 ounces. Feel free to hit the stamp more than once, but hold that stamp steady, making sure you don't shift at all between hits. The more confident you are with the hammer and the strength behind it, the better your impression will be.

Product name: She Believed She Could So She Did Stainless Steel Charm - Laser Engraved - Round - Quantity Options - F4L4
Description:
You will receive these "She Believed She Could So She Did" made to order LASER engraved stainless steel charms.
Measurements are 1" x 3/4" or 25mm x 20mm (vertical x horizontal).
Perfect for charm bracelets, pendants, necklaces, earrings, piercings, key chains, zipper pulls, bookmarks, or anything else you can think of!
The charms are created with a high quality, hand polished stainless steel that is hypoallergenic and won't tarnish. 
We have our own fiber laser engraver that we operate right here in New Mexico!
To watch our laser engraver in action, check out our video:
youtube.com/watch?v=RocGxQIOXS4
Our laser burns deep into the charm, which brings out the dark bold tones of the metal. The end result looks very professional and will not fade since we don't use any aerosol paints or chemicals in our lasering process (the fiber laser is very powerful).
With regular "etching" or engraving with an etcher, it only scratches the surface of the metal and leaves a white hard-to-read finish. Since we use a lasering process, the design will be easy to read and clearly legible in any light.
Check out our Instagram for videos of our lasering process! (Link is at bottom of description)

Product name: Stiletto Matte Swarovski Nails | Press On Nails | Fake Nails | False Nails | Glue On Nails | Acrylic Nails | Handpainted | Nail Art
Description:
Simple and gorgeous.  A purple hued taupe gets the matte treatment and is accented by two crescents of genuine Swarovski crystals on the ring fingers.  The ultra glamorous stiletto shape adds to the drama.  
**Crystals will be on the size 5 nails, unless you request otherwise.**
The set of 12 will include a range of sizes that should fit most fingers - 0,1,2,3,4,5,5,6,6,7,8,9 (the width measurements are below, so please check before you order!)
If in doubt, move up and get the full set to ensure you have the sizes you'll need.
Size 0 : 1.5 cm
Size 1 : 1.3 cm
Size 2 : 1.2 cm
Size 3 : 1.15 cm 
Size 4 : 1.1 cm 
Size 5 : 1.0 cm 
Size 6 : 0.95 cm 
Size 7 : 0.9 cm 
Size 8 ; 0.8 cm 
Size 9 : 0.7 cm
Nails have been filed, painted, given a coat of topcoat, and then a final coat of gel topcoat and cured under a UV light to prolong wear without chipping.  Any crystals or rhinestones have been set with an industrial bonder.  The full set of 20 nails should fit most nail beds with minor adjustments.  You'll want to completely remove any old nail polish or oils and gently push your cuticles back before applying, to ensure a good fit. 
Included in your box will be a small "make ready" kit, consisting of an alcohol wipe, an orangewood stick, and a nail file.  I don't include glue or tabs with the listing, but they're readily available at most beauty stores.  If you break any, or would like a few more spares, message me and I can quote you for replacements.

❥Kindly use the zoom function on the pictures provided as the smaller versions that populate on screen can be a bit grainy, however the zoomed photos are clear.
═Super Slim Notched Curved Spacer Band═
We designed this spacer band with a very slight notched curve. It features a mid-section clearance of ~1mm. This is popular with ladies who have rings with main center stones whose setting protrudes ever so slightly from the base where it meets the ring shank so that a traditional spacer ring without a notch would not sit flush with the main ring. When properly paired, the lower part of this spacer ring will sit flush against your main ring, while the notched portion curves daintily around the base of the setting of your main stone.
✧Ring size selection:
Recommended ring sizes are provided in the selection menu. If you would like a different size, simply select the "My Size Preference" option and use the notes section during checkout to leave us your preferred ring size. Kindly take a bit of care when wearing this ring in a size larger than recommended.
✧Wearing Style category: Spacer Band
Spacer band definition: A band created with a super slim profile both in width and height used to add a touch of space between two other rings. Spacer bands are not recommended as stand-alone rings although many ladies do enjoy them as such. Kindly exercise a bit of care if wearing this ring as a stand-alone fashion ring.

Description:
Hand-cut, sanded for perfectly smooth edges, hammered or plain, these rings are made to last a lifetime! They are very sturdy, lightweight and comfortable; ideal for everyday wearing.
They are timeless and totally versatile when it comes to style. Each can be layered with other rings for a Boho chic look, or worn solo as a bold & modern statement piece. 
★ HOW ARE THESE RINGS CUSTOMIZABLE? ★
You can customize your own ring by choosing its width and texture. 
To figure out which width is most suitable for you, measure the distance between the knuckles of the finger you will wear it on. For width comparison, see images 3 & 4.
You can choose from 4 different widths:
1.5 cm (0.6") tapered or non-tapered back *
2 cm (0.8") tapered back
2.5 cm (1") tapered back
3 cm (1.2") tapered back
* Tapered back means they are shorter from the back. This makes them comfortable when you bend your fingers. The backs of all tapered rings measure 0.8 cm (a little more than 1/4")
You can choose from 4 different textures / finishes:
Satin (plain  matte)
Mirror (plain  polished)
Stone (hammered  matte) 
Shine (hammered  polished) 
★QUALITY & MATERIAL ★
All our jewelry is made from highest quality STAINLESS STEEL
* NEVER tarnishes

* Very sturdy

* Lightweight
Due to its sturdiness, aesthetic appeal and high resistance to corrosion, stainless steel makes our jewelry ideal for everyday wearing. Our rings will not bend out of shape with long heavy wear and are meant to last a lifetime. 
None of our jewelry is plated, which means it will not fade or chip over time.

want to save this for later? click Save to Favorites!
want to share with your friends? click LIKE to share on Facebook!
*******************************
*what is gold filled?
Gold filled is a hollow tube of usually 14K gold that is filled with another metal. The exterior of the gold filled jewelry is solid karated gold and everything you can see or touch is a solid layer of karated gold.
This tube of karated gold is approximately 100 times thicker than gold plate. It is made by bonding with heat and pressure - with normal wear and tear the karated gold will never tarnish, chip or wear off. By law this layer of karated gold has to be at least 1/20 of the total weight of the metal portion of the piece of jewelry.
Many jewelry purchasers outside the jewelry trade mistakenly think 'gold filled' is the same as 'gold-plate'. 'Gold filled is a much higher quality product.
As less gold is being used gold-filled or rolled gold jewelry is a cost effective alternative to karated gold jewelry.

Product name: Black Obi Belt / Sash Oriental Japanese Geisha style by loobyloucrafts ... Kimono Yukata belt wrap ... Standard size
Description:
Looby Lou obi belt
This is my standard size obi belt.
It adapts well to different waist measurements.
Recommended for a waist measuring 25 inches to 32 inches / 63.5 cm to 81 cm.
I have too longer options of this black belt in my shop if you would a longer version :)
My Looby Lou obi belts are inspired by the Japanese obi but I have adapted them for the modern women! They are easy and comfortable to wear. They can really give an outfit that extra wow factor and individual twist.
Here are a few style suggestions:
-  go traditional and wear one with a kimono  
-  wear with a long flowing skirt or dress for a festival boho look
-  go ethnic and tie your obi over harem style pants
-  be elegant and wear it with a pretty dress 
-  for a smart look wear with a blouse and skirt
-  or be casual with denim jeans/shorts and t shirt 
the possibilities are really endless ..... as is the way you tie your obi belt! 
The front panel is pleated into the ties. This gives the obi belt a unique shape, creating small folds that make it easy to wear whilst being versatile.
It is great for cinching in the waist! The ties can be tied at the back or can be wrapped around and tied at the front. There are so many ways to wear this belt - have fun with it!
Made from a plain matt black cotton mix fabric.

Product name: Personalized Leather Belt / Deer / Wildlife / Free Name
Description:
This belt has deer in a wildlife scene embossed and antiqued.
It is made out of a solid leather strip of 100% cowhide.
***All our belts are made to order and will be ready within 5 business days***
Sizes 30 and up are 1  1/2" wide and have a rope border.
Sizes 20" - 28"  are 1  1/4" wide and have a single crease border.
    We can put up to 8 letters in the name space or we can make them without a name space.The name is free. Please spell the name you would like on your belt in the notes section on the PayPal page .If you do not want a name please request" no name space" on the notes section.          
    When ordering your belt go up one size from your pant size. ( for example : a person that wears a 34 pant will need to order a 36 belt.) If you have a buckle you want to wear with you belt, keep your belt the same size as your pant size.( The buckle will add an extra size.)
 ** If adding a bigger buckle, order your pant size, do not go up a size!**
              This is an approximate size chart for our belts;
  Belt size  -------------- Kids Pant size
    20"   ------------------- 18month-2T

    24"   -------------------  6 - 7
    26"   -------------------  8 - 9
    28"   -------------------  10 - 12         Jr/Misses sizes     Men pant size

    32" ---------------------  14 - 16 ------------- 3/4  -----------------  30"

We do make bigger sizes!!
  All of our belts are handmade in our shop in NW Florida. We start with 100% solid leather blanks. There are over a dozen steps in the creation of these belts, all of which are completed in our shop. Belt edges are beveled in order to provide more comfort and prevent cutting into clothing. 
  Belts are dyed and treated with several finish and top coats in order to provide colorfastness and durability. Belt edges are dyed and treated in order to provide more protection to the leather and add to the appearance of the belt. All belts are provided with a leather keeper and a standard harness buckle but are finished off with snaps at the buckle end in order to allow changing of the buckle if desired.
  
   Our goal is to provide a quality leather accessory that will provide many years of service. We have been doing this for almost fifteen years. We sell locally and work many craft shows annually and have many customers that buy from us repeatedly and look for us every year to fulfill their personal and gift needs. We stand behind our products and strive for repeat customers. If you are dissatisfied in any way please contact us and we will work with you in order to achieve your satisfaction.
